{"word":"H8231 - שָׁפַר - shâphar - shaw-far' - [idiom] goodly","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁפַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâphar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-far'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] goodly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நேர்த்தி, அலங்கரி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be pleasing, to be beautiful, to be fair, to be comely, to be bright, to glisten; (Qal) to be beautiful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>glisten</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>fair: - </i> X goodly."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7782 - שֹׁופָר - shôwphâr - sho-far'/7782\">H7782</a>, <a href=\"#/H8208 - שָׁפִיר - Shâphîyr - shaf-eer'/8208\">H8208</a>, <a href=\"#/H8231 - שָׁפַר - shâphar - shaw-far'/8231\">H8231</a>, <a href=\"#/H8233 - שֶׁפֶר - shepher - sheh'-fer/8233\">H8233</a>, <a href=\"#/H8234 - שֶׁפֶר - Shepher - sheh'-fer/8234\">H8234</a>, <a href=\"#/H8235 - שִׁפְרָה - shiphrâh - shif-raw'/8235\">H8235</a>, <a href=\"#/H8236 - שִׁפְרָה - Shiphrâh - shif-raw'/8236\">H8236</a>, <a href=\"#/H8237 - שַׁפְרוּר - shaphrûwr - shaf-roor'/8237\">H8237</a>, <a href=\"#/H8240 - שָׁפָת - shâphâth - shaw-fawth'/8240\">H8240</a>"}]}